title: Looking for a duo partner to mess around in low elo
body:
Hi, unranked now hit b2 last season and not looking to grinde that much but to mess with somone new playing off meta picks or strats that are good. Like gp, retired supp main and I play every role. (Dont like mid) Add me "Hacksource9000" ill relpy as soon as i can. Cheers 
Ps: I play lol mainly for fun not to win so keep that in mind.

replies.body:
Hey bro, lookin' for some sick duo partner. You're probably a pleb so doesn't really matter if we lose a few games right? Haha, anyway, if you want to be my duo partner, I'll be happy to. (I'm currently silver 4).

- Guy next door
